{"tid":1730901,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"兩張漫畫圖就可以完美解釋到點解唔可以係Ycore走","createTime":"2019-11-17T15:12:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T15:31:31.000Z","uid":48315,"like":74,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"4b98b0cd7fd7b5e02071d07678f2a676b30063ed","tid":1730901,"uid":48315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T15:12:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mPsxnSs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmPsxnSs.jpg&h=d608436a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8gejNi9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8gejNi9.jpg&h=560aaf42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一個好簡單既心理學<br />\n當人覺得自己無得走 就會用盡全力抵抗 <br />\n但當有人發現有少少走既希望 就會完全放棄抵抗 最後比人拉哂<br />\n<br />\n先唔講佢地會唔會衝入大學先<br />\n係國際方面 入大學拉哂啲人個畫面實在太樣衰<br />\n同埋美國人權法聽日無人反對就會過<br />\n班警曱衝入去大學無論係國際定香港人眼中都係無法原諒既事<br />\n<br />\n所以有可能班警曱就係用呢招<br />\n叫你係呢條路走 然後手足就會衝去果條出路<br />\n結果無人守 同時離開果條路又會比人拉哂<br />\n<br />\n所以以家唯一可以救到手足既方法就係要人多 人多 <br />\n反包圍班警曱 要令佢地撤退 手足先可以走到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0165e218a9fd35f8265d737112a4fd872e37d6c6","tid":1730901,"uid":125502,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T15:13:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L5J4Yo9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL5J4Yo9.jpg&h=3a1a4096&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"04dab5d44a7a88906c282d685ecc1e80fefdbba9","tid":1730901,"uid":264963,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4b98b0cd7fd7b5e02071d07678f2a676b30063ed","tid":1730901,"uid":48315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T15:12:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mPsxnSs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/